<a class='dk-social-btn-unit dk-social-btn twitter-share' href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailykos.com%2Fstory%2F2010%2F10%2F12%2F909826%2F-&amp;text=ZERZETSEN+TORTURE+-+Spooks%2C+Lies+and+Threats+'>
<span class='dkons icon-twitter'></span>
<span class='dk-social-count'></span>
